item.description: .NET Conf is an annual conference dedicated to the world of Microsoft's .NET framework and related technologies. In 2023, .NET Conf promises to be an exciting event, bringing together developers, engineers, and tech enthusiasts from around the globe. Attendees can expect a dynamic program filled with informative sessions, keynote presentations, workshops, and networking opportunities.At .NET Conf 2023, participants will gain insights into the latest developments in the .NET ecosystem, including updates on .NET 7 and other cutting-edge technologies. They will have the chance to connect with industry experts, learn best practices, and explore practical use cases through hands-on demonstrations. item.title: .NET Rocks! Applied Large Language Models with Vishwas Lele
item.description: How do we put large language models to work? Carl and Richard talk to Vishwas Lele about his work using LLMs with his customers. Vishwas talks about focusing on specific data sets for building LLMs and how size matters - things are simple when the source data is small, but as it grows, you need more complex tools to be able to allow the LLM to perform. Lots of cautionary tales and ideas on how to get great results from these new automation tools!
